Treatwell Gift Cards are prepaid vouchers that allow you to purchase online services onhttps://www.treatwell.be/and on our app, which features numerous hair salons, beauty salons, and barbershops. Treatwell Gift Cards are a convenient way to enjoy a wide range of beauty and wellness services.
Validity:Treatwell Gift Cards are valid only in Belgium.Expiration:The Gift Cards expire on the date indicated on each card.Usage:They can be used for all services available on treatwell.be and the Treatwell app.